document_data.mainbody:
arette Oberon was a Lady patron of the arts from the Oberon patriar family of Baldurs Gate in the late 15 century DR.
During the Absolute crisis of the , Lady Harette Oberon was invited to attend the art show titled "Strange Tides Self-Portraits from the Sword Coast," hosted by Lady Jannath in her Lower City estate. Harette RSVPd to attend with a plus one guest.
